version_description: Additional chords, as Paolo plays it. Neat, concisely formatted. Chord legend included.

All of the lyrics are included, with the chords above them, and chords are placed more accurately over lyrics. Is also a slightly different version of the song, not the live version, but the album version.
Corrected chord placement, seperated song into sections, added strumming pattern (based on ukelele in the recording) and other information.
Complete and well-aligned chords for the whole song including instrumental parts / suggestions for playable voicings.
